smart-text doesn&#39;t support switch-to-tab yet,  but if you need it or something else feel free to mail me (or open issue on tracker) and i&#39;ll try to implement it

also if you need help with creating custom style for this i&#39;ll be happy to help
hope you&#39;ll like this addon, and will write lots of reviews;)

&lt;i&gt;versions 4.5 and 4.6b2 beta bellow 
work with latest nightlies
and are compatible with status4evar&#39;s latest version (Status-4-Evar 2011.04.06.18)
also they have improved options dialog and support for non unicode domains

